snippet.title: Welcome to Toro's Friend Network!
snippet.description:
Toro's Friend Network is a free-to-play app for the PlayStation®Vita in which you can meet new friends and expand your social network!

Guided by PlayStation's mascot Toro, connect with others on the PSN, Facebook, and Twitter.

Toro's Friend Network is available 6/4/2013.

http://us.playstation.com/psvita/games-and-media/psv-toro-s-friend-network.html
